  "title": "Cannot un-refine a selected Menu item",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\n\r\nA bug.\r\n\r\n**What is the current behavior?**\r\n\r\nWhen instantiating a `Menu` React component, I expect a click on a refined item to remove the refinement. It's not the case so far.\r\n\r\n**If the current behavior is a bug, please provide all the steps to reproduce and a minimal\r\n[JSFiddle](https://jsfiddle.net/) example or a repository on GitHub that we can `npm install`\r\nand `npm start`.**\r\n\r\n```js\r\n<Menu attributeName=\"category\" />\r\n```\r\n\r\n - Click on an item -> refined\r\n - Click on the same item -> SHOULD un-refine\r\n",
